'''Bella Agossou'''  wavutse 1981 ni umukinnyi wa filime wo muri [[Bene|Bénine]] muri sinema zo muri [[Esipanye]].  

== Umwuga ==
Agossou yatangiye umwuga we muri [[Benin]] nk'umukinnyi w'amafirime hamwe na sosiyete "Sonangnon" yaremye kandi itezwa imbere na we. Icyakora, nyuma yimyaka 4 ashinze isosiyete, yimukiye muri [[Espanye|Espagne]] mu 2002.  Nyuma yize indimi z'Igikatalani n'Icyesipanyoli kugira ngo akore umwuga wo gukina filime. Yakinnye muri filime ''Un cuento de Navidad'' (Christmas Tale) afite uruhare runini rw’umugore ushakishwa na polisi kubera kubura impapuro nk’abimukira batemewe. 

Nyuma, yakinnye cyane mu mafilime menshi yo muri [[Afurika]] no mu mahanga harimo ''Los Nuestros'', ''Moranetta'', ''A cuento ya Nadal'' na ''Palmeras en la Nieve'' . Ku ya 13 Nyakanga 2017, Agossou yeretse abanyamakuru iduka ryitwa "NOK". 

